text.tspan: The DEMOS tool originated in the context of two research
projects (FACTORS and DASCOM) dealing with software
complexity. The DEMOS tool is based on a new declarative
model – the EP-model – that possesses the following features:
it has a small metamodel; it supports a graphical notation;
finally, it allows executable models to be described by annotating
model elements with code snippets. By leaving complex parts at
the code level this hybrid approach achieves executability while
keeping the basic modeling language simple. Learn More...
